===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|bold}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|bold}}, {{m|ang|blod}}, {{m|ang|bolt}}, {{m|ang|botl||house, dwelling-place, mansion, hall, castle, temple}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*budlą}}, {{m|gem-pro|*buþlą||house, dwelling}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*bʰew-||to grow, wax, swell}}. Cognate with {{cog|ofs|bold||house}} (whence {{cog|frr|bol}}, {{m|frr|boel}}, {{m|frr|bøl||house}}), {{cog|frr|bodel}}, {{m|frr|budel||property, inheritance}}, {{cog|gml|būdel||property, real estate}}. Related to {{l|en|build}}.

